              Membekali peserta didik dengan kompetensi di bidang jaringan
              komputer, server, cloud, keamanan jaringan, dan IT support
              sesuai standar industri.
            </p>

            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
              <li>Jaringan Komputer & Internet</li>
              <li>Administrasi Server</li>
              <li>Cloud & Virtualisasi</li>
              <li>IT Support & Troubleshooting</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tata Busana -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="/images/jurusan/tata-busana.png"
            alt="Jurusan Tata Busana"
            class="w-74 h-74 mx-auto mb-4 object-contain"
          />

